   <abstract>This postcard has two copies and each of them shows a side view of the Home of Renfro Valley Barn Dance building. Verso reads: The big Renfro Valley Barn is the scene each Saturday night of one of the most unique radio broadcast on air today-The Renfro Valley Barn Dance. On many occasions more than ten thousand visitors have stood in line to gain admittance to the show. With each card having other information about the people they were addressed to.</abstract>
